attachments.title: Google's Head of Allo and Duo confirm Hangouts isn't going anywhere (for now)
attachments.text: Amit Fulay, Head of Allo and Duo, confirmed on Twitter that Hangouts for consumers isn't going anywhere, but changes to Allo are on the way so we'll need to "stay tuned".
